info.name: EventSquid API
info.description:
Complete API collection for EventSquid Private API

Authentication:
- Session: Use headers `cftoken` and `cfid`
- Dev Token: Use header `devtoken`
- Public endpoints: No auth required

See docs/AUTHENTICATION.md for details.
